<main class="w-100 mx-auto p-1">
  <h1 class="text-center">{{ site.title }}</h1>
  <blockquote>
    <p>Protest art itself doesn't create change, but it aims to embolden and galvanize enough people across socio-economic
      backgrounds to mobilize for a cause.</p>
    <footer>â€”Deva Pardue, graphic designer</footer>
  </blockquote>
  <p>
    <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Protest_art">Protest art</a>
    is an important tool of activists and social movements. It can inform and inspire. It comes in a variety of shapes and
    forms: signs, banners, posters, and other printed or hand-made material.
  </p>
  <p>
    These are just few powerful examples.
  </p>
  <div id="gallery" class="pswp-gallery pswp-gallery--single-column">
    {% for image in images %}
      <div class="pswp-gallery__item">
        <a href="{{ image.src }}" data-pswp-width="{{ image.width }}" data-pswp-height="{{ image.height }}" target="_blank">
          <img src="{{ image.src }}" title="{{ image.title }}" alt="{{ image.alt }}"/>
          <div class="pswp-caption-content">
            {{ image.caption | safe }}
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</main>
